Title: Plumber Power
Description:
Not all leaky pipes accessible from outside. Some inside tunnels run all under Gundargaz.

Tunnels small for stoneheads, but kobolds love tunnel! Just need someone to show layout. You, someone.

Check with crew boss if have problems. He help go over maps.
ObjectivesText: Use the Tunnel Access to plot the steam pipe routes through Gundargaz.

Objectives.Text: Tunnel Rat Crew Boss spoken to
